Notes:
  • GPU 1D / GPU 2D times are attributed from the shared forward pass
    proportionally to node count (n_1d / (n_1d + n_2d)).
  • 'Wall total' covers the entire autoregressive rollout (all T steps),
    including Python overhead and CUDA synchronisation.
  • Seed-ensemble ×3 multiplies wall time by ~3 (models run sequentially).
  • Zone-bias correction and XGBoost post-processing are CPU-only and
    not included here; see their respective scripts for those costs.
